### Room Endpoints

### Get all rooms
GET {{baseUri}}/api/rooms

###

### Reservation Endpoints

### Check room availability
POST {{baseUri}}/api/reservations/check-availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "startTime": "2025-12-01T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-12-01T11:00:00Z"
}

###

### Create a reservation (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUri}}/api/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "title": "Team Meeting",
  "description": "Weekly team sync",
  "startTime": "2025-12-01T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-12-01T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Get all reservations
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations

###

### Get reservations for a specific room
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations?roomId=1

###

### Get reservations for a date range
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-31

###

### Get my reservations (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations/my
Authorization: Bearer {token}

###

### Get a specific reservation
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations/1

###

### Update/Reschedule a reservation (requires authentication)
PUT {{baseUri}}/api/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Team Meeting",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "startTime": "2025-12-01T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-12-01T11:00:00Z"
}

###

### Cancel a reservation (requires authentication)
DELETE {{baseUri}}/api/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {token}

